      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or chip, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth engine and transmission that perform exactly as intended. A buyer can expect a vehicle that requires zero maintenance or cosmetic attention, offering a like-new driving experience.",
