    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical reliability and structural integrity. This acquisition provides an optimal balance of sophisticated aesthetics and proven durability, making it a compelling choice for those who demand quality without compromise.",
      "price": 31500.0,
